Getting Started

    You can start a TrueVFS application project
    {{{./maven.html}with}}
    or
    {{{./no-maven.html}without}}
    Maven by following the respective guide in the menu on the left of this
    page.
    Once you've setup your project, you should read the short
    {{{./tutorial.html}tutorial}} to learn about the client APIs.

    Whether you use Maven in your project or not, the
    {{{../truevfs-archetype/truevfs-archetype-access/index.html}TrueVFS&#160;Archetype&#160;Access}}
    sets up a template project for you with some fully-working example
    applications in five minutes.
    If you want even more sample code, then there is the module
    {{{../truevfs-samples/index.html}TrueVFS&#160;Samples}}.
    Please
    {{{../truevfs-samples/source-repository.html}check out}} or
    {{{http://repo1.maven.org/maven2/net/java/truevfs/truevfs-samples/${project.version}/truevfs-samples-${project.version}-sources.jar}download}}
    its source code.
